ant across the file is eq_const k=~2.1e-27).\n\nUpstream test reproduction: the inline test `upstream_arrplus_ppb` pins k at the parameter defaults to the value asserted by the `@testitem \"arrplus_ppb\"` block in GasChem.jl test/geoschem_ratelaws_test.jl, which compiles the rate law at T=293.0 K and num_density=2.7e19/N_A*cm3_m3 mol/m^3 and checks the resulting rate constant k."
