                {
                    "id": "upstream_rate_PAN_abab",
                    "description": "Reproduces the upstream `rate_PAN_abab` rate-law test (GasChem.jl test/geoschem_ratelaws_test.jl). All parameters are at their declared defaults \u2014 the exact coefficient values the upstream @testitem passes to `rate_PAN_abab` \u2014 and the rate coefficient k is pinned to the upstream expected value 0.00017076882173869417.",
